title: Bloomberg Markets 12/9/2025
description: "Bloomberg Markets" follows the market moves across every global asset class and discusses the biggest issues for Wall Street. Today's guests: Nationwide Mutual Chief Economist Kathy Bostjancic, Bloomberg's Bailey Lipschultz, Tyler Kendall, Crystal Tse and Nishant Kumar.  (Source: Bloomberg)
